((P\wedge Q)\vee (\neg P \wedge \neg Q))\iff((P\Rightarrow Q)\wedge (Q\Rightarrow P))\tag{1}
((P\wedge Q)\vee (\neg P \wedge \neg Q))\iff(\lnot P \lor Q)\wedge (\lnot Q \lor P))\tag{2}
